Sorry you're having trouble here. Unfortunately, the TensorFlow maintainers do not currently have the bandwidth to support builds on Windows (see https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources), so we won't be able to help you out here and rely on community support for this.

If you are able to resolve this, we would encourage you to send a pull request so that others can benefit. Thanks!
